Package it.unitn.disi.sweb.names.model

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    EType
    Entity implementation class for Entity: EType Class representing an type per an entity.
    FullName
    Entity implementation class for Entity: FullName Class representing one of the possible name for an entity.
    IndividualName
    Entity implementation class for Entity: IndividualName Class representing an individual name, which can compose a full name.
    NamedEntity
    Entity implementation class for Entity: Entity Class representing an Entity.
    NameField
    Entity implementation class for Entity: NameField Class representing the fields that an individual name can represent (example: firstname, surname).
    NameToken
    Entity implementation class for Entity: NameToken Class representing the relation (N to N) between FullName and IndividualName.
    Translation
    Entity implementation class for Entity: Translation Class representing the dictionary where are contained all the tranlsation in the system.
    TriggerWord
    Entity implementation class for Entity: TriggerWord Class representing trigger words, which are words part of a full name, but does not represent a name.
    TriggerWordEType
    Entity implementation class for Entity: TriggerWordEType Represents the relation between the trigger words and etypes.
    TriggerWordToken
    Entity implementation class for Entity: TriggerWordToken Class representing the relation (N to N) between FullName and IndividualName.
    TriggerWordType
    Entity implementation class for Entity: TriggerWordType
